    "type": "message",
    "text": "I watched one of Jon Blow's live streams once and the audience did actually spot a few bugs. This is just via YouTube live chat which is a terrible communication medium. I think there's legs in the idea of Twitch-meets-GitHub type platform, just needs good tooling for filtering out crap.",
